WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.520
Nicely done. I'm actually a

2
00:00:02.520 --> 00:00:04.920
little scared of how easy
 all this information was found.

3
00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:08.200
Do us all a favour
 and make sure it doesn't happen again.

4
00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:12.360
Better turn on two factor authentication
 to make it harder in future.

5
00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:16.840
Since most websites have it, 
it's practically a guarantee FriendlyBook has.

6
00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.080
The app should already
 be installed on the phone.

7
00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:21.360
Switch it on. Check it works.

8
00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:22.880
And then we can put
 this whole thing to bed.

